      "content": "\"letting some of that pressure go\"... i dont know. it just feels like every time i try to fix something, it just breaks more. the more i struggle, the deeper i sink. it feels like the world is just closing in on me and i'm just... done. i'm just so tired of the cycle. it feels like the only way to actually stop the feeling is to just make it stop. for good.",
